{"tid":813811,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆唔比我買電競keyboard","createTime":"2018-09-10T17:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T10:22:11.000Z","uid":140503,"like":28,"dislike":127,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"2ebf6e6dd9ee7f62881921d13d1857b47d8721f0","tid":813811,"uid":140503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:31:20.000Z","msg":"話說小弟今年16歲<br />\n16歲係青少年反應最快嘅時候<br />\n好多人會走去玩d咩足球啊籃波啊<br />\n而我就當然玩依家最hit嘅電競驚lol<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日用電腦節買番黎嘅特價電競滑鼠上左金5<br />\n想叫老豆買埋電競keyboard比我乘勝追擊上埋白金<br />\n點知老豆又食古不化<br />\n話d咩電競沒撚用 傻仔先玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我已經唔係要電競椅啦<br />\n個個同學仔都有電競keyboard啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解我要個電競keyboard都唔得啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我點上白金鑽石做職業選手啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043de53d9968a5be40cadb76ff4b184220b61168","tid":813811,"uid":146756,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:32:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"17ab8b13841cf116d38db381f1725b12d1f38fab","tid":813811,"uid":140503,"like":8,"dislike":25,"score":-17,"quote":{"pid":"043de53d9968a5be40cadb76ff4b184220b61168","tid":813811,"uid":146756,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:32:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:33:56.000Z","msg":"有電競keyboard加電競椅我就做到電競選手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲洗讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711ce1cb81b6881a925c1f3781c6ba1caea215ff","tid":813811,"uid":115579,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:35:28.000Z","msg":"返學啦仲玩"},{"pid":"3ec672fe36782dcaf38af40735cf7119918e8038","tid":813811,"uid":59857,"like":0,"dislike":0